dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Vernon County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Vernon_Roads_2018.gdb'. [This data set consists of digital map files containing road centerline information obtained predominantly by heads up digitizing off of ortho imagery, and through previously created datasets maintained by Vernon County. Features contained in the data set include all road centerlines countywide and associated attributes and annotation.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
